# Devno
The bot for my Discord community


### Updates [v0.3.7 alpha]
DevnO is currently uncompatible to the discord api. We are currently fixing this issue.

### Installation
The currently available installation methods are:
Python    -Manual installation 
Docker    -We are currently developing a stable docker image

You can find a full step-by-step guide on installing DevnO on our WiKi[https://airpathoncode.github.io/wiki/devno.html]

